text: Abbie Stockard (born July 26, 2002) is an American beauty pageant contest who won Miss America in 2025. Stockard won Miss Alabama 2024, making her the fourth woman from Alabama to win Miss America. Stockard is in a relationship with basketball player Walker Kessler. ==References== Category:2002 births Category:Living people Category:Miss America winners Category:People from Birmingham, Alabama
